#How to use
#Setup venv for security

# Create venv for folder called .venv
python3 -m venv venv

#Activate the venv
source venv/bin/activate

#install required packages
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install telethon python-dotenv

Then edit env file

Edit all according

Then edit py file

Edit ENV_PATH 

For cron
Then run py file 

venv/bin/python3 file.py /path/to/folder
